if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">6. 前往警署慰問警員</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支持良心警 黑警濫權可恥 害群之馬破壞警隊形象<br />\n支持成立獨立調查委員會 還警察一個清白</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n隨POST附上打飛機文比各位阿蛇<br />\n世警會觀眾撐港隊高呼<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「雄<span style=\"color: brown;\"><del>勃</del></span>起」</span></span> 網民：速龍勁過飛虎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/361764/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E4%B8%96%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E8%A7%80%E7%9C%BE%E6%92%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%9A%8A%E9%AB%98%E5%91%BC-%E9%9B%84%E8%B5%B7-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E5%8B%81%E9%81%8E%E9%A3%9B%E8%99%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F361764%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A7%2580%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%2592%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259A%258A%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%2591%25BC-%25E9%259B%2584%25E8%25B5%25B7-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E9%2580%259F%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%258B%2581%25E9%2581%258E%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%2599%258E&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzUYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=71467e0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/361764/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E4%B8%96%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E8%A7%80%E7%9C%BE%E6%92%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%9A%8A%E9%AB%98%E5%91%BC-%E9%9B%84%E8%B5%B7-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E5%8B%81%E9%81%8E%E9%A3%9B%E8%99%8E</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:01:32.000Z","msg":"整靚返啲 Links<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/政情/361745/逃犯條例